## Mutation Testing

### Stryker Setup

```bash
npm i -D @stryker-mutator/core @stryker-mutator/vitest-runner
npx stryker init  # generates stryker.config.mjs
```

```javascript
// stryker.config.mjs
export default {
  testRunner: 'vitest',
  mutate: [
    'src/**/*.ts',
    '!src/**/*.test.ts',
    '!src/**/*.d.ts',
    '!src/types/**',
  ],
